<title>USA: FTC ends wait on Constellation's Imo bid.</title>
<headline>FTC ends wait on Constellation's Imo bid.</headline>
<dateline>RICHMOND 1997-08-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Constellation Capital Partners LLC said Friday the U.S. Federal Trade Commission has granted early termination to the Hart-Scott-Rodino Act waiting period regarding its II Acquisition Corp affiliate's tender offer for all the outstanding stock of Imo Industries Inc.</p>
<p>The company said the offer includes Imo's associated series B junior participating preferred stock purchasing rights.</p>
<p>The company said the offer is set to expire Aug. 27.</p>
